 Placid in 1988 doing trail and bike maintenance, then road-raced bikes and worked as a mechanic at Serotta custom bikes, Steiner's Sports, Blue Sky Bicycles, and Alpine Sport Shop in Saratoga Springs. After moving to Telluride he served as General Manager of Paragon Ski and Sports, built carpentry at Bill Ward Construction for a decade, and from 2020 worked as property manager at Valentine Farm and Jubilee Stables. He played Lizard Head hockey throughout."}],"slug":"peter-hazard-1964"}},"burialCemetery":null,"institutionsById":{},"crossConnections":[]}